{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"- ("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"removeAnnotations:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:Q$objc(cs)NSArray","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSArray<id<MLNAnnotation>>"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"annotations"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"name":"annotations","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The array of annotation objects to remove. Objects in the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"array must conform to the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol."}]}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Removing annotation objects dissociates them from the map view entirely,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"preventing them from being displayed on the map. Thus you would typically"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"call this method only when you want to hide or delete the given annotations."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"metadata":{"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(im)removeAnnotations:","symbolKind":"method","title":"removeAnnotations:","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"removeAnnotations:"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"removeAnnotations:","kind":"identifier"}],"r